title: Can't Post! Says I'm still level 5! Please help!
body:
It shows I'm level 5 but I've actually been doing ranked for a couple or so weeks now.

Please let me post on the boards. I've sent a ticket but that didn't help. Glad I realized I can at least make a post here.

Your help is much appreciated!

replies.body: If you're posting for the first time, it can be a bit for your account to sync to the boards.  Everything looks fine now, though!
